      },
      "date": "2012-06-21 11:39:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Fails\n\nOn Lustre 1.8.8-wc1 node:\n\n# mkfs.lustre --reformat --fsname=testfs1 --mdt --mgs --param=\"mdt.quota_type=ug3 mdt.rootsquash=500:500 mdt.nosquash_nid='10.10.4.131' mdt.group_upcall=/usr/sbin/l_getgroups\" /dev/sdc5\n\n    Permanent disk data:\n Target:     testfs1-MDTffff\n Index:      unassigned\n Lustre FS:  testfs1\n Mount type: ldiskfs\n Flags:      0x75\n               (MDT MGS needs_index first_time update )\n Persistent mount opts: iopen_nopriv,user_xattr,errors=remount-ro\n Parameters: mdt.quota_type=ug3 mdt.rootsquash=500:500 mdt.nosquash_nid='10.10.4.131'  mdt.group_upcall=/usr/sbin/l_getgroups\n\n device size = 9546MB\n formatting backing filesystem ldiskfs on /dev/sdc5\n         target name  testfs1-MDTffff\n         4k blocks     2443880\n         options        -J size=380 -I 512 -i 2048 -q -O uninit_bg,dir_nlink,huge_file,flex_bg -E lazy_journal_init -F\n mkfs_cmd = mke2fs -j -b 4096 -L testfs1-MDTffff  -J size=380 -I 512 -i 2048 -q -O uninit_bg,dir_nlink,huge_file,flex_bg -E lazy_journal_init -F /dev/sdc5 2443880\n Writing CONFIGS/mountdata\n\n# mount -t lustre /dev/sdc5 /mnt/mds\n\n# umount /mnt/mds\n\nAfter upgrading to the Lustre build with contains the patch, mounting the MGS/MDT succeeded. However, dmesg showed that:\n\n Lustre: 7373:0:(obd_config.c:1334:class_config_llog_handler()) For 1.8 interoperability, rename obd type from mds to mdt\n Lustre: testfs1-MDT0000: used disk, loading\n Lustre: 7373:0:(mdt_handler.c:4836:mdt_process_config()) Found old param mdt.quota_type, changed it to mdd.quota_type.\n Lustre: 7373:0:(mdt_handler.c:4843:mdt_process_config()) Found old param mdt.rootsquash, changed it to mdt.root_squash.\n LustreError: 7373:0:(obd_config.c:1174:class_process_proc_param()) Can't parse param ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ (missing '=')\n Lustre: 7373:0:(mdt_handler.c:4851:mdt_process_config()) Found old param mdt.nosquash_nid, changed it to mdt.nosquash_nids.\n LustreError: 7373:0:(obd_config.c:1174:class_process_proc_param()) Can't parse param ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ (missing '=')\n Lustre: 7373:0:(mdt_handler.c:4829:mdt_process_config()) For 1.8 interoperability, skip this mdt.group_upcall. It is obsolete.\n Lustre: 7367:0:(mgc_request.c:1518:mgc_process_recover_log()) Process recover log testfs1-mdtir error -22\n\nI'm investigating the above issue.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
